Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:46.86,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(498,0)}Can't focus. My body is still puzzled about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.62,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'm trembling. I can't stop even if I try to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:54.37,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Although neither sun nor moon are on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.79,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}"I've no choice but to try,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.46,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Those were the words I muttered to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:04.05,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}The odds aren't on my side, but running way'd be gutless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:08.05,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}Even if I can't see the future, I'll just have to win it over with courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:11.55,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Need to keep distance from the target as I hold myself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.85,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}All that's needed for victory is pride to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.93,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Will we celebrate with the wine of victory
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.94,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Or'll we end up kissing their feet in defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.69,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}There are two outcomes to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.40,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}I want to control destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.74,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I need to seize the golden opportunity with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:38.83,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll finish it up with my best poker face,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:43.75,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,458)}And drag them into a world of illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:50.13,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll find my way out of this endless pressure game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:54.14,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}And leap over the borderline of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:58.85,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}How many? What'll I need to sacrifice to make it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:03.11,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,500)}What is the one thing I don't want to let go?
