Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:06.42,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't find warmth on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:11.93,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)}By meeting you, I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:17.77,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}How much strength love could give me.
