Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:33.53,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't sleep by myself, 'cause I can't dream without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:39.29,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}So take me to a place where uncertainty can't reach us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:44.55,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}And let us bring light to the night sky with no stars.
