Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:17.66,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Meiyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I need to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.90,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just give them a pat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.77,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,They're your kids, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.40,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to become monsters like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:57.16,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, if it were something you could "catch" like a cold, I would have become one a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.79,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I've witnessed many deaths since gaining this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:11.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to suppress the sadness by telling myself that death is just a speck in the grand scheme of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:18.72,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx98}Whenever I'd witness something beautiful or wondrous, I'd accept this body, thinking it'd give me time to see them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.68,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it's always been for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:26.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Until I met you and had kids, Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:34.94,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I never age, but I'm watching\Nmy kids age and grow like trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.95,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrified all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.99,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me that I truly am a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:47.92,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.46,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, come here for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.38,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.38,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.51,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A photographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.34,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Try to look nice, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.35,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,We've never taken a family portrait before, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But this is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.86,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.57,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.66,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Please take the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.66,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.67,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Face this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.79,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:38.42,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You know... someday, I'll turn into a wrinkled old woman who looks like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:45.31,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how I end up looking, I'll always be happy to take a picture with the family where everyone is smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.43,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stay with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.56,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't distance yourself from us and leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.94,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt yourself by saying you're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.20,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.45,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:23.64,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to accept this body and continue living like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:26.60,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:35.69,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I want to age and die with Trisha and the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.28,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.84,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.67,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Fixing the swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.76,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You're not really used to these things, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:07.80,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do a single thing for them, so I wanted to at least do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:13.06,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Trisha, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.60,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.57,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.07,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the kids about my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.24,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.20,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to say goodbye to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.33,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,If I see their faces, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.42,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You blockhead. It's okay if you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:47.22,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, why are you two up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al says he needs to go pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:53.18,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were looking after Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.14,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.27,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.37,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,No, I still can't reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:17.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... we can't contact the guys at base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.83,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Should we keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There should be an exit somewhere to toss the rubble that was dug out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going for just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Smith, you go back to report on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:28.96,Default,Smith,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.35,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in a perfect, immortal army?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.90,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,No death, no decay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.40,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.32,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cut him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.45,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that the idea is so wild; I don't know how to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.95,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two choices:\NYou're either interested, or you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.12,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:53.84,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So when that day comes, not just I,\Nbut my men will also be able to benefit from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.97,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,When that day comes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.60,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So he can't guarantee that much, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:06.14,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If I accept their offer, they'll force me to assist them in causing a bloodbath at Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:12.11,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,And if I decline, they'll put someone else in charge of the base, and I'll most likely be demoted or reassigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.11,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I wonder what my best option is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.62,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.16,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The advance unit that went into the underground tunnel-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.46,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,What about the underground tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.30,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:32.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something has happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.59,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.76,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.47,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to be tied up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.07,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this, Buccaneer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.28,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently transferring the Elric Brothers from the east cells to the west cells, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.16,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that gentleman, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.54,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Solf J. Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.42,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,He's Lieutenant General Raven's guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:12.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee... So he's the Crimson Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:17.17,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers... So you must be the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.80,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see why you were given that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.35,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since anyone's made that mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.49,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact with the platoon that went to investigate the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:48.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And soon after, Smith's horse came back with an arm presumed to be his.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.25,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Just his arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.46,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What about his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.13,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Missing, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.51,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The horse he was on is too worked up\Nand can no longer be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.59,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Henshel, send in a rescue party imme-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.55,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.47,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,That hole is far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.73,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with that biological weapon you were talking to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.61,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Put him back into the tunnel and\Ncover up the hole, Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.99,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,But our men are still-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.36,Default-alt,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to the Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.57,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the law here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:28.33,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Obey the ones with power, Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.88,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Raven from Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.13,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard everything from the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.26,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've been keeping your mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We promised, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.93,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:55.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be strange to be happy after having people taken hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... when can we get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:03.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The deal was that we'd be able to continue\Nour journey as long as we didn't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.99,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll get you out of here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That hole... it's also a part of your plan, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.58,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:22.13,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Major General Armstrong agreed to returning\Nthe Homunculus in the tunnel and sealing the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.51,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,The Major General joined forces with us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.27,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.19,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to search for the missing unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.44,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Henshel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.40,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,But they may still be alive and need assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.82,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I said, silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.69,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,"Obey the ones with power", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:54.00,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So even the impregnable "Northern Wall of Briggs" has to give in to authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.08,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the smart approach to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.14,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So that's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.02,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.73,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.69,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.61,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.78,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. You still have some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.28,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Pride tell you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.28,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:35.29,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,It's a drag... but I have to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.59,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,What a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.17,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it a drag again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.43,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to remember is a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.81,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:58.44,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,He's a chimera that's performing a task for the Central Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.94,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,He's working to make this country stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.32,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still a top-secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.82,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Now, cover up this hole, my friends at Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.66,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You all are kindred spirits who I've shared my secrets with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:32.43,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The essential parts have been replaced with ancient Ishbalan, so I can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.26,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't help that, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.85,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,If Scar were here, we might be able to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:41.86,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,If he's an Ishbalan monk, there's a chance he'd know the ancient language.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:48.03,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened to Mr. Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl carrying a black and white cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.83,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.17,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Scar! Sir Yoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.05,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the research documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.43,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.05,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's switch locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.39,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers from Briggs have already found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.56,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.40,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:31.70,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,We, the chosen ones, will be granted a body close to God's, and we'll rule this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.32,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Was his name Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.20,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can be done about the advance unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.87,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So the weak should become victims for the chosen ones to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.75,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Survival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:50.01,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,The weak become the foundations of a nation, and the strong prosper above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.43,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So Ishbal was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.68,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.22,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal was also a part of our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.93,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Those weak people were destined to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.56,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.61,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.07,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.94,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.12,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly make a lot of phone calls, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.16,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Lieutenant General Raven?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.79,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:31.55,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the verge of death, but you somehow managed to make a recovery on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.72,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic spell did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.47,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:41.22,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, you were jailed for killing officers. How did you manage to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.48,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has this plan been in motion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.69,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it's been in motion since this country was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.41,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll finally be complete during my generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:59.49,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your cooperation, Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.45,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'll negotiate with the higher-ups and prepare a seat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.83,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.00,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:15.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Smith's left arm? Or his right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.01,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:22.35,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Aging is truly horrifying, isn't it, Lieutenant General Raven?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:28.40,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you used to be a young, dignified soldier who loved this country from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.31,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.44,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You have the chance to become a chosen one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.86,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I promised you a seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.53,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for another seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:42.04,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking the seat your rotten ass has been sitting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.46,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You useless geezer!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:57.63,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Immortality... is right in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:04.14,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You can lie there and literally become a foundation of this base, Lieutenant General Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:08.35,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted... to become immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.77,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Buccaneer, contact Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.52,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.86,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else, continue working as if nothing's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.86,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,General.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.49,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.37,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth the concrete, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.37,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.91,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You're being very pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:32.29,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm a State Alchemist who served in the Ishbalan War?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.92,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.59,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know what kind of deaths your people experienced?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.89,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.01,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:45.01,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She says, "Mission complete.\NYou don't need to buy any more time."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.03,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.11,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.66,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I'm relieved from talking with that freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.41,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was putting on an act, it was exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:09.79,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.58,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Lieutenant General Raven is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.17,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to know where he'd be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.38,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.13,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:24.18,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,The base isn't built safely enough for people to just walk around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.31,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to the Lieutenant General-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That's good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:38.28,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I received permission from the Führer President to act independently if something happened to Lt. General Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:43.16,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Could you drive me down to the base of the mountain, Major Miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:51.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,My orders right now hold equal importance to those of the Führer President's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.92,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.51,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Before you cover the hole completely, please send in a search squad for Smith and the unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:07.43,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The Fullmetal Alchemist created a secret passage in case a situation like this arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Raven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.73,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's all I needed to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When the hell are you guys going to let us out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:24.07,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Ask the Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Getting impatient won't do us any good, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:30.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important to rest for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:35.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay put when so many things are going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.55,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.93,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to speak with the Fullmetal Alchemist-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:50.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It seems as though I'm not very popular here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought a guest today for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.03,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.03,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,To switch your automail to the kind they use up here, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys in jail, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No one called you out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.29,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.13,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have known if the people from the military hadn't told me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.13,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The military?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.13,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:25.63,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President was very worried to hear of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:01.48,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:02.69,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:06.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from a friend who works as a nurse at the foot of Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:08.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He was hospitalized with serious injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:12.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,but his wounds were healed right after Lieutenant General Raven came to visit, and he was released right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:15.91,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Raven and Kimblee...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all the information I have for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:20.66,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:23.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for your help again when I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stop by at the shop again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.18,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You were dumped, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.85,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you buy some flowers and chase after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:37.26,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:38.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:42.10,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There are women who will dump you, but there are also women who are looking for a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.52,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from\NMajor General Olivier Mira Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:49.11,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Roy Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:54.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be buying all of those flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:03.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The chain binding them appears in unusual form.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:07.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, unbind the chains and wrench them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:11.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Reel it in and expose the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:16.18,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:20.72,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 37, The First Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.18,0:24:23.60,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Stratagems and blackmailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:26.52,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the measures taken to fulfill one's desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.39,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)}13 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.93,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,0)}A Few Days Later
